  Almost every after market degree pully I have seen uses a 10 width belt
and after there are used up to an 11. Most of the aftermarket degree pulleys
have a different angle and width V groove in them. I have found that Gene
Bergs and SCATS are the best. EMPI, Bugpack and all the rags mag ad ones are
pure crap. Latest Rages heavy degree pully is awesome with the correct
groove and depth and also are balanced perfect

ronnie

