Well I have a number of 1500 and 1600 engines about and all of the stock
pulleys and this degree pulley are the same diameter.>
7 inches nominally..
the degree pulley is very slightly smaller at edge but is is constructed a
bit differently and I think it makes the belt ride right down in the
groove whereas the stock pulleys the belt doesnt seem to sit all the
way down.

